        <img id="drx-partner-gif" src="/assets/images/projects-ct-6.png" class="br-100">

        <h4 class="container-fluid tc">Advocate</h4>

        <p class="tj">
            Help fellow bartenders fulfill original ideas into reality. We believe no idea is too complex to be achieved, no matter how crazy it may seem!
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container fl w-25-ns">
        
        <img id="drx-partner-gif" src="/assets/images/projects-ct-5.jpg" class="br-100">

        <h4 class="tc container-fluid"> Backer </h4>
        <p class="tj">
            Become a sponsor in any project! Just sign up and choose your contribution.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class=" container fl w-25-ns">
        
        <img id="drx-partner-gif" src="/assets/images/projects-ct-1.jpg" class="br-100">
        <h4 class="tc container-fluid"> Creator</h4>

        <p class="tj">
            Help fellow bartenders fulfill original ideas into reality. If the project funds, you'll receive exclusive pre-launch gifts !

        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container fl w-25-ns">
        
        <img id="drx-partner-gif" src="/assets/images/projects-ct-4.jpg" class="br-100">
        <h4 class="container-fluid tc">DRNXMYTH</h4>
        <p class="tj">
            Dial DRNXMYTH for Drinks: Make your recipe fly, far away with our partner's state of the start beverage creation model!
        </p>
